                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 893.00/1134.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-03-03T10:00:00+08:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 3, 1912—10 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The 200 American troops have arrived. Serious mutiny, with looting and burning,
                    at Tientsin last night.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Calhoun.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
